hat laissez faire approach was rolled back to today=E2=80=99s policy ( http=
s://help.x.com/en/managing-your-account/about-x-verified-accounts ) that re=
quires review for non-deceptiveness (and which includes special badges like=
 Breton=E2=80=99s gray check-mark for being a government official), but the=
 fact remains that X=E2=80=99s potential fine is actually a lot lower than =
that suggested in the excerpt, because the company=E2=80=99s advertising re=
venue has never recovered. That certainly seems like the market is working!

More broadly, one of the the critiques of European economies is how difficu=
